snippet.textDisplay:
At first I thought this song to be as one of the other songs of this season. It is more interesting to know about the history, why this song was written and then listen to the song.
It is painful, yet melodious. Wonderful voice and she sang it so beautifully knowing the history of the song, that's why the character came alive with some addition made by her and approved by Rohail Haytt so gracefully.
One of the best product of this season in Coke Studio.♥️👍🏻

snippet.textDisplay:
India claims the entire erstwhile princely state of Jammu and Kashmir based on an instrument of accession signed in 1947. Pakistan claims Jammu and Kashmir based on its majority Muslim population, whereas China claims the Shaksam Valley and Aksai Chin. 


And all that Kashmir claims and need is peace. May peace and happiness prevail in Kashmir soon❤
